strings: <voice_0x01000F28><se_def>The prince Carlos: I'm finally home. After the last long journey, life is like this.
<voice_0x01000F2A><se_def>The prince Carlos: Raise your flag! Yes, the markets are open! Without us, everything would have started!
<voice_0x01000F2B><se_def>The prince Carlos: Shop before returning to the castle on the left!
<voice_0x01000F2C><se_def>The prince Carlos: If we retreat to the castle, we won't have time to use the commodity market... ah!
<voice_0x01000F2D><se_def>The prince Carlos: I'll be back tomorrow, today I'm going to rest at the hostel. Don't worry, I'll pay you poor guy.
